channel.title: How do I make a 667/711 client?
channel.description: Ok I have a 711 cache without the chatbox problem, and I've put it in the server so it loads that cache but how do I make my 667 client run the 711 cache? I'm new again to this stuff because I haven't coded in nearly 2 years so help would be appreciated :)
